{"tid":2498963,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母大家小心趕飛機嘅日本人","createTime":"2021-04-21T13:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T15:50:05.000Z","uid":140587,"like":19,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"d876b70a91cd0f586c7531a309a200c37c6a719d","tid":2498963,"uid":140587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:50:29.000Z","msg":"首先我認自己係弱智on9咁都可以中伏<br />\n<br />\n啱啱旺角有個講日文嘅人話唔識路去朗豪坊，我做好心人帶佢去，途中佢俾咗日本電話俾我，仲話要喺朗豪坊附近搭E21去機場趕八半飛機返日本，我同佢講巴士會趕唔切，不如搭的士，截到的士原來佢得百五蚊，然後捉住我隻手又喊曬口問可唔可以借200蚊，話之後還返俾我。佢扮得好撚似，又留咗電話，我on9信咗。<br />\n<br />\n事後諗落唔對路，睇返原來一早有人中過伏，仲要係十年前嘅技倆，2021年應該得我先會咁弱智會借錢俾陌生人出機場，大家如果再喺旺角遇到有講日文嘅人話唔識去朗豪坊直接屌佢老母就得，呃我錢條撚樣我祝你不得好死。<br />\n<br />\n十年前其他人中招嘅link<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=8243384\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.discuss.com.hk%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D8243384&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dOQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=0d002ef3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=8243384</a>"},{"pid":"24a5875abe666eb618dd57b21c9ce9b7cd6cd6a7","tid":2498963,"uid":180402,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:51:25.000Z","msg":"睇中香港人崇日心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf9cfd11e5a8aa654b0247542e3c5cc0e9212ba","tid":2498963,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24a5875abe666eb618dd57b21c9ce9b7cd6cd6a7","tid":2498963,"uid":180402,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:51:25.000Z","msg":"睇中香港人崇日心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T13:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4ce78982fd0b9de58c7feb4491fe272195957a","tid":2498963,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021